name: Born A Hippie
description: There is nothing like a free spirited hippie with a sky blue bow to make you smile. Birthday cake patterned print with pearlescent buttons and orange gems. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Peonies and Jealousy
description: Don't let the nasty green monster take over your day. Smell the peonies and get back to enjoying the smaller things in life. A large emerald green daisy bow with an aged silver sunrise filigree and faceted gems. Brooch and alligator clamp back Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Dream On Cerulean
description: Sometimes we just have to keep holding on to that one single dream. Made out of vintage cerulean floral printed bubble bow with found buttons and gorgeously sculpted rose cabochons. Brooch and alligator clamp back. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Floating Whimsies
description: Delicate like all the dandelions whimsies floating past with wind. Feel as carefree with this pink laced bandeau, adorned with frosted pink beads, and vintage rose cabochon. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Vintage Bonanza
description: Made from the same lusciously beautiful floral print like our Briars in the Gems in a stretchable bandeau. Positively soft, and perfect for an afternoon stroll. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Captain, Oh Sailorly
description: It's a look worthy for a ocean smart First Mate! A wonderfully exquisitely navy and crimson striped print on a stretchable black bandeau. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Blackbird Momentarily
description: Something that every woman should have. Much like the classic little black dress, this is the perfect black bow for any occasion. No frills, and entirely svelte. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: A Letter for B
description: Who is B? B is the long lost love, the one that got away. The one that still brings nostalgia and stinging, unrequited. Vintage soft pink rose print and vintage pearl buttons. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Venus Snare A Boy
description: A boy ain't no match for one determined femme! She'll ensnare you with her allure and charms just like this flamboyant polka dotted hairband. Accented with silver wing filigrees, teal ribbons and vintage yellow cabochon. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: It Isn't Easy Being Green
description: Vintage rose tattoo print double bow bandeau, with a fierce edge. It definitely it isn't easy being green when its this strong willed. Stretchable black bandeau. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Unusual Suspects
description: Get your thinking caps on and think like a famous detective. Solve the murder mystery with such style and flair with this lime green bandeau. Stretchable black bandeau. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Candy Strickers
description: Its bright like a swirly lollipop, and almost as sugary sweet. Made out vintage striped prints and an orange sherbet ribbon. Brooch and alligator clamp back. Approximately 5 inches in length. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Rhines Cowgirl
description: Giddy up, and wake up to a fierce rodeo. A blue and black vintage patterned print with black leather studs and sparkling rhinestones. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: A Bit of A Social Butterfly
description: Sipping a caramel macchiato in a some artsy cafe, and updating your Twitter. A perfect lunch means an awesome meal chatting with some old friends. A sweet butterfly beige pattern bow on a bandeau, that is oh-so adorable. Stretchable black bandeau. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Sunrise Summer
description: An over sized bright summery bow, with a tropical patterned print. Its loud and bright like summer dress, perfect for lounging around poolside. Barrette style back. Bow is approx. 7 inches in length. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Teal We Meet Again
description: Its a party under the palms! A festive gold, purple, and teal oversized bow, with a fierce jagged edge. Perfect for adding an additional pomp to any summer outfit. Barrette style back. Bow is approx. 7 inches in length Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Chili and Peas Please
description: The sizzling black version of our Minnie's Rain Shower hairband. Its innocently sweet yet fierce at the same time. A wonderfully polka dotted bow adored with a vintage silver pea charm and a golden lotus filigree, on a slim hairband. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Jagged Demure
description: Shy and innocent, with a daring edge. This large sheer bow is flashingly accented with a spiked glass bead and other found items mounted on black hairband. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Blue Valentines and Silver
description: Sometimes we only get one chance, and end up with the blues. These vintage rose patterned bobby bows may be blue but it will certainly perk you up with its lovely silver LOVE charms. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Bad Girls Club
description: Who wants to be a goody two shoes when its so easy to be oh so bad? Consider this your invite to join the dark side, with a black poof bow adorned with a fierce silver panther and pink leopard thunderbolts. Barrette styled back. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Pink Hearted Petals
description: A much more coiffed and demure sister to the Purple Hearted Vintage, this barrette style bow is set against a soft flower print. Accented with a pink heart gem that glistens with a chocolate cabochon. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Purple Hearted Vintage
description: A hair bauble bursting with valor, and quite proud at that. Soft pink vintage prints are fiercely juxtaposed with a found heart gem and flower cabochons. Barrette styled back. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Soul Freaks
description: A throwback to all the funk and pomp of the 70s, with this neon pink fishnet bow. Adorned with an aged Queen Elizabeth coin and a bubble bell, its ready to dance till dawn at the disco. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Gold Neon Lighted
description: A fresh turquoise and teal patterned bow paired with a vintage gold button lights up anyone who wears this fun headband. Finishing of this funky look are some found gems and florals. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Briars in the Gems
description: A golden rose tucked exquisitely between vintage print fabric in stunning royal blues. Inspired by the soft feminine wiles of the chic woman, who looks like a walking goldmine. Part of the Wunderkinblitz Collection.

name: Double Trouble
description: Adorable vintage lily pad, with a silver singing frog charm. Set on a pair of bobby pins. Inspired by the Harry Potter series.

name: Sneakoscope
description:
Charmed bracelet made out of shimmering and pink spinning beads, on a glistening silver chain... its almost magical. Inspired by the Harry Potter series.

Part of the Fantastique Fantasie Collection

name: Hired Armored Bears
description:
Deux fantastique! These dashing pair of armoured bears are set on golden studs are sure to impress even Lord Byrnison. Inspired by The Golden Compass / Northern Lights

Part of the Fantastique Fantasie Collection

name: Alethiometer's North
description: Bearing the vintage living tree button, its super soft felt plays sharp contrast to the baubles adoring it. Large enough to securely hold a ponytail in place. Inspired by The Golden Compass / Northern Lights

name: The Snow Queen
description:
Icy at heart, and mean as a bonafide queen... this snowy phone charm is sure to give your gadgets a bold attitude. Made out of vintage pearls and buttons. Inspired by Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, The Witch, and The Wardrobe.

Part of the Fantastique Fantasie Collection

name: Creamsicle
description: Delightful as a scoop of vanilla ice cream on a warm sunny day. This ivory tinted bunch of beads are perfect for a fun day at the beach, as well as an elegant night out!

name: Cotton Muslin Favors
description: A wonderfully exquisite 100% cotton drawstring bags, perfect wrappings for any bauble. A delicate drawstring secures your items for gifting on any occasion! Specifications Small -- 3 x 5" Meduim -- 5 x 6 1/2" Please add this listing for each item.

name: Kraft Gift Boxes
description: Say hello to a greener earth, enclose your to be gifted items in 100% recycled eco-friendly gift boxes! Please add a quantity for each item you would like to be placed in a gift box. All gift boxed items will be packaged alternatively to maintain its pristine condition. Specifications Small -- 2.5cm x 1.5cm x 0.70cm Medium -- 3cm x 2cm x 1cm What are you waiting for? Its perfect for that special someone! Please add this listing for each item.

name: Customized Gift Wrapping
description: Wrap it for that special someone! We take the hassle and wrapping woes out by offering customized wrapping services. Add a quantity for each item you would like to be wrapped. Contact us for paper and ribbon selections currently available. Each season we feature a different array of wrapping paper for your convenience!

name: I Wanna Hold Your Hand
description: Beautiful vintage pearls strung into a simple yet elegant bracelet. The copper and matte vanilla finish on each bauble is sure to adorn when worn!

name: Inspired by Circumstances
description: The accompanying bracelet to our My Everything necklace. Its pearl and agua tinted baubles are perfectly simple yet functional.

name: Know My Name
description: Featured handknit tangerine wool baubles, adorn with multicolored beads to accent this fun and funky dangling earrings.

name: Harder to Breathe
description: Peachy pearls and seashelled stars adorn this cute pair of dangling earrings.

name: Everybody's Sweet
description: Striped tangerine baubles with peach hued pearls on a dangling pair of earrings. It actually looks as if each bead is floating when worn!

name: Sweet Smell Freedom
description: Be free and be rebellious with our beaded nectarine baubles. Each has been handbeaded and adored with tangerine tinted beads, lovely and luscious!

name: This Love
description: Cherry red and oversized heart studs! Its fun, funky and fierce to be sure and indelibly inspired by Maroon 5's This Love song.

name: Blossomed None More
description: Tangy yet subtle. This pair of dangling earrings are sweet and simple.

name: Fluffberry
description:
Super soft and multifunctional! Our exclusive fluffberry cellphone charms clean your screen and also decorates your phone as well. Comes adorned with a cute little bell.

Available in seven colors!

name: Super Fluffberry
description: An oversized version of our popular fluffberry cellphone charms! Made out super soft multicolored pastel yarns, its a perfect little way to clean your phone.

name: Cherish Cherries
description:
Adorable cherries for those double pierced gals everywhere. Made out of lucite cherry charms and silver chains.

Its cherrytastic!

name: Superfly 75
description: Vintage translucent disco balls... that was long phrase! But this kickback to the 70s adds the perfect dance beat to your everyday style.

name: Wish Upon A Star
description: Subtle yet cute bell charms for your cellphone. Comes in two color combination.

name: Little Octopus
description: Specially for double pierced pirates, arrh! This cream and tan colored bauble is inspired by squids and octopuses alike, and is definitely a league of its own.

name: Celestial Ink
description:
Plucked from the heavens, these ivory hued stars would look brilliant dangling from your ears... really! Flanked by coppery golden baubles that shine like the sun.

Perfect for a day on the sand!

name: Raspberry Choco Parfait
description:
Back in college I read this certain guy's shirt, it blared out "I've never met a chocolate that I didn't like." It was cute and subtly funny.

Now this is one chocolate themed earrings you won't be able to resist... especially with its raspberry and candied baubles.

name: Goodness Citrusy
description: Tangy and lemony bits and baubles in this summer themed pair of dangling earrings. Perfect with a glass of lemonade, a good fashion magazine, and a porch on a summer day.

name: Little Miss Sunshine
description:
She's the reluntant beauty queen, all smiles and all that. She's the kind of girl that would cheer you up like no other, when everything is all gloomy.

That's the spirit behind this yellow lucite dangling earrings.

name: For The Love of My Life
description:
A hodgepodge of random items fashioned into a darling pendant charm, corralled by a silver chain. 

Inspired by the many things in life that one can treasure.

name: Penguin Loves Elegant
description:
Charming noir inspired beaded cellphone charm, with vintage buttons and baubles.

Its the elegant meets the devious... this isn't your pudgy villain of Gotham!

name: Bluebird's Nest
description: Especially handcrafted from silver wires and swarovski crystals, this bluebird sure knows how to sing. Pearlescent blue baubles decorate this decadent hair pins.

name: Sunshine Fairy
description: Let the sunshine fairy brighten your day with a little whiff of her sunlight wand! Vintage ephemera is the theme for this one of a kind bobby pin, made from an old stock sheet from the 1920s.

name: Notebook Scribbles
description:
Remember when there weren't any blogs, instead it was diaries and journals galore. This homage to the good ol' times is taken from Courtney Love's own scribbles.

Its rockstar meets school chic!

name: Glistening Crimson
description: Multifaceted ruby bauble on an adjustable ring. Sweet and simple, yet glistening.

name: Floral Regality
description:
Vintage poppy flowers framed by a silver filigree, delicate and regal.

Available in two color schemes.

name: Cherry Blossoms
description: A wire bookmark that blossoms as it unfolds on your favorite page. Use it to keep track of your reading... its so subtly built that it won't ruin even the most delicate of vintage books.

name: Big Soft Heart of Mine
description: Uniquely handcrafted cuff bracelet with vintage buttons and ephemera.

name: Let Them Eat Cake
description: Inspired by the fierce Marie Antoinette herself, this decadently handcrafted cuff bracelet is adorned with vintage ephemera from the 1940s.

name: Cherry Cherry Mon Ami
description: Earth friendly we are, with this green inspired handcrafted cuff bracelet. Adorned with lucite buttons, fancy stars from an old trinket box.

name: Sweethearts Are Golden
description: Undeniably sweet, we treasure these kind of girls that are a treasure amongst the crowds... the veritable girl next door. This handcrafted cuff bracelet are dedicated to that girl -- she's not only a bestfriend but a sweetheart as well.

name: Love That Is Alive
description: Features a very special living tree vintage button from a Los Angeles dressmaker circa 1950s. It was said that this certain femme seamstress took so much care in her work, inspired by her doting husband. Handcrafted cuff bracelet.

name: Metallic Pink Hearts
description: By day she's a docile librarian, by night a rocking bassist. Inspired by all the girls who transform themselves, and are not afraid to show it. This finely handcrafted cuff bracelets feature a vintage heart button as its centerpiece.

name: Rose Colored Life
description: All sails from a nautically inclined femme! Striped patterns and metal badges are the natural inspiration for this beautifully handcrafted cuff bracelet. All vintage ephemera circa 1950s.

name: Care Bears Pillows
description:
Lusciously soft handsewn pins featuring technicolored Care Bears. Perfect for pining to a jean blazer, or to your favorite tote. Inspired by the modtastic stylings of 1980s.

Available in four colors.

name: Little Miss Kitty
description: An adorable caricature of our favorite cartoon cat! Inspired by old cartoons in technicolored TV sets back in 1980s.

name: Which Way is Love?
description:
Oversized hadsewn fabric pin that is perfect for a lapel, or your favorite canvas messenger bag.

Show him that you are the one to be loved!

name: Jump Ringo
description: Lets rock and roll with one of the best and brightests from across the pond... matte metal earrings and glass baubles featuring an old photograph of Ringo Starr from the Beatles. Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: Checker Denim
description: Inspired by the stylings of Daisy Duke, this denim and checkered glass bauble studs are sure to ride to the rodeo. Giddy yap, cowgirl! Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: Shiny Silver Bass
description: Reminiscent of socialite tea parties and debutante, this is the rebellion against the prim in proper. A silver chained necklace with vintage gem charms. Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: Love x Cobain
description: Oversized clip on earrings featuring rock enthusiasts Courtney Love and Kurt Cobain, immortalized on glass baubles. Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: Decked Duran Duran
description: A memory from childhood includes finding a beaten up tin box containing original Duran Duran pins. Transformed into this handmade adjustable ring with a glass bauble. Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: Material Girl Remade
description: Adjustable ring featuring a young Madonna, encased in a glass bauble and decorated with a silver leaf detail. Truly exquisite! Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: Blue El Roy
description: Inspired by the bold lines of Roy Lichtenstein's Drowning Girl, this handmade adjustable ring pokes fun on the seriousness evoke in pop culture artwork. Its a fun (and mockingly seaside) twist with a vintage starfish and glass baubles. Part of the Midnight Collection.

name: A Star Is Born
description: Handcrafted from an vintage Madonna poster, this adjustable lovely ring features glass baubles and a brushed silver star. Hanging from the star is a translucent lucite charm. Part of the Midnight Collection.
